name: Fred the Frog
overview: Fred the Frog from Robert W. Benjamin requires you to eat insects to enable you to progress through the stages. The problem is during your journey you have to avoid bees, birds, seagulls, knives, bottles etc as one hit and it's game over and back to the 1st level you go. The game requires patience as the 1 hit and it's game over is a bit tough.
